0.query:
fetch spans
| filter isNotNull(request_attribute.TSN) and in(k8s.namespace.name, $Environment)
| filter contains(request_attribute.LTN, "Astroshop")
| makeTimeseries { average=avg(duration)}, by: { request_attribute.TSN }, time: start_time, bins:250
| append [
  fetch spans
  | filter isNotNull(request_attribute.TSN)
  | filter contains(request_attribute.LTN, "Astroshop")
  | makeTimeseries { requestCount=count() }, time: start_time, bins:250
]
0.title: AVG Response Time by Step - 300s timeout

12.title: Exceptions

15.query:
fetch spans
| filter isNotNull(request_attribute.TSN) and in(k8s.namespace.name, $Environment)
| filter contains(request_attribute.LTN, "Astroshop")
| fieldsRename requestName=request_attribute.TSN
| summarize { 
  requestCount=count(),
  failedRequests=countif(request.is_failed),
  average=avg(duration),
  median=median(duration),
  p95=percentile(duration, 95),
  p99=percentile(duration, 99),
  max=max(duration)
  }, by: { requestName }

18.query:
fetch logs
| filter in(k8s.namespace.name, $Environment)
| filter k8s.namespace.name == "astroshop"
| filter status == "NONE"
| parse content, """(IPADDR:'http.client_ip' | [! \n]+):host
' ' ('-' | NSPACE:ident)
' ' ('-' | (DATA{1,8096}:auth >>(' [' HTTPDATE)))
' ' '[' HTTPDATE:event_time ']'
' ' (('\"' [A-Z-_]+:'http.method' ' ' LD{0,8096}:uri ' ' LD{3,10}:'http.flavor' '\"') | DQS:invalid_request)
' ' LONG:'http.status_code'
' ' (LONG:'http.response.content_length' | '-')
(' ' DQS:referer (' ' DQS:user_agent)?)?"""
| fields http.status_code, timestamp
| makeTimeseries count(), by:{coalesce(toString(http.status_code), "unknown")}
18.title: Logs By Level

28.query:
fetch spans
| filter isNotNull(request_attribute.TSN) and in(k8s.namespace.name, $Environment)
| filter contains(request_attribute.LTN, "Astroshop")
| fieldsAdd duration=duration/1000/1000
| makeTimeseries { 
  count=count(),
  countFailures=countIf(request.failure_rate),
  average=avg(duration),
  median=median(duration),
  p95=percentile(duration, 95),
  p99=percentile(duration, 99)
  }, time: start_time, bins:250
28.title: Response times vs Request count

4.query:
fetch spans
| filter isNotNull(request_attribute.TSN)
| filter contains(request_attribute.LTN, "Astroshop")
| filter in(k8s.namespace.name, $Environment)
| summarize Spans = count(), by:{request_attribute.LTN}
| parse `request_attribute.LTN`, """DATA:TestTool "-" DATA:TestName"- VU("INT:VU") Loops("INT:Loops") - " TIMESTAMP('d MMM yyyy HH:mm:ss'):formattedTimeStamp"""
| fields TestTool, TestName, LaunchTime=formattedTimeStamp, Spans

40.query:
fetch bizevents
| filter event.provider == "dynatrace.site.reliability.guardian" AND event.type == "guardian.validation.finished"
| filter contains(guardian.name, "astroshop staging quality gate")
| fields timestamp, guardian.name, validation.status, execution_context, validation.summary, validation.errors
| parse execution_context, "JSON:execution_context" | fieldsFlatten execution_context | fieldsRemove execution_context
| parse validation.summary, "JSON:validation.summary" | fieldsFlatten validation.summary | fieldsAdd validation.summary.total = validation.summary.pass+validation.summary.warning+validation.summary.fail+validation.summary.error | fieldsRemove  validation.summary

// Final fields
| fields timestamp,
  status=if(validation.status == "fail", concat("🛑 - ", validation.status), else: if(validation.status == "warning", concat("🟡 - ",validation.status), else:concat("✅ - ", validation.status))),
  health= if(validation.summary.fail!=toDouble(0), toDouble(0), else: (toDouble(validation.summary.pass)/toDouble(validation.summary.total))*100.0),
  guardian.name,
  execution_context.build_version,
  execution_context.problem  
  // validation.summary.pass,
  // validation.summary.warning,
  // validation.summary.fail,
  // validation.summary.error
40.title: Median
